                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Balt.</placeName>\n                                        <date>July 9. 1848.</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your letter of the <date>5.</date> should\n                                        have<lb/> been answer<add>?</add> immediately but as the\n                                        documents<lb/> you required were in <placeName>N\n                                                  York</placeName> it was necessary<lb/> they should\n                                        be order<add>?</add> here to procure <persName>Mr\n                                                  Ansel'</persName><lb/> endorsement. The forthwith\n                                        will for <add>?</add> on<lb/> my application. They arrived\n                                        yesterday, and<lb/> I now enclose them to you that you may\n                                        at<lb/> once relieve your C. H bond. Thus your<lb/>\n                                        differences are all closed. If you write<lb/> soon to the\n                                        owner of the Goods, you will say<lb/> that\n                                                  <persName>Myer</persName> had no disposition to\n                                        retain<lb/> the articles or the proceed of sales from\n                                        him<lb/> it has seem<add>?</add> to be a mistaken point\n                                        of<lb/> ettiquette.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With kind remembrance to<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mrs. Cozens</persName> and our frd. <persName>Mr\n                                                  Florence</persName>\n                                        <persName>Aunt Grace</persName> &amp;. &amp;. &amp;.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\"><add>?</add> Truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(12)\">\n                                        <add>?</add>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">David Judah</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pg1j495/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
